sourcesContent:
export default {
  destinations: [
    {
      name: "AsthenosphereSE",
      slug: "astheno",
      image: "astheno.jpg",
      id: 1,
      description:
        "AsthenosphereSE Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Reactor Room",
          slug: "astheno1",
          image: "astheno1.jpg",
          description:
            "This map is very simple. You'll want to split up your team, so you have two players defending each side, and two at the back. Throughout the whole map. E.g. 'Player A & B Green side, Player C & D Red side, me (E) back Green, remaining (F) back Red'"
        },
        {
          name: "Observation Lounge",
          slug: "astheno2",
          image: "astheno2.jpg",
          description:
            "Watch out for jumpers going high. Push out as far as you can if you're not back defence."
        },
        {
          name: "Final Area",
          slug: "astheno3",
          image: "astheno3.jpg",
          description:
            "Here you can switch it up to have one watching high with sniper. Attackers can come from the vents, and the first time they go through you'll get a warning message."
        },
        {
          name: "Escape",
          slug: "astheno4",
          image: "astheno4.jpg",
          description:
            "The one at the back needs to get good incomings, and watch the lift where attackers can go down."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "AutoRIP",
      slug: "auto",
      image: "auto.jpg",
      id: 2,
      description:
        "AutoRIP Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Despatch Doors",
          slug: "auto1",
          image: "auto1.jpg",
          description:
            "One player (A) in the sniper nest, one watching the tunnel on the right side (B), and one backman (C). If attackers jump into vents, the backman is supposed to be watching the drop down point."
        },
        {
          name: "Development",
          slug: "auto2",
          image: "auto2.jpg",
          description:
            "One in the window (backman high) (A), one at the top of the stairs (backman low) (B). One in front of Test Room (C), two across the laser bridge (D & E), one low in front of the stairs (F), keeping an eye out for attackers coming up the ramp (x)."
        },
        {
          name: "Bomb",
          slug: "auto3",
          image: "auto3.jpg",
          description:
            "Tactics aren't usually given for this part, but you'll want people pushing as much as possible, and one watching the Test Room exit."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Ballistic",
      slug: "balli",
      image: "balli.jpg",
      id: 3,
      description:
        "Ballistic Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Main Gate",
          slug: "balli1",
          image: "balli1.jpg",
          description:
            "Attackers can set hammer launches from (X) to the Main Gate, and from (Y) to (Y1). Backhammer from (Z) to (Z1)."
        },
        {
          name: "Generator",
          slug: "balli2",
          image: "balli2.jpg",
          description:
            "Two players in front of the Generator (A & B), one at the vials (C), one on the bunker watching jumpers and rocketshot (D) and the other two push. If attackers breach the nest, bunker and one of the forward pushing people suicide and chase. E.g. 'A & B gen, C vials, D bunker, E & F push. If they breach nest, D and F suicide and chase.'"
        },
        {
          name: "Warhead Loader",
          slug: "balli3",
          image: "balli3.jpg",
          description:
            "One backman low (A), one backman high (B), one in the tunnel (C), one standing at the window (D), two pushing out the window (E & F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Final",
          slug: "balli4",
          image: "balli4.jpg",
          description:
            "One on the globe (A), one in the side room (B), rest push out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Bridge",
      slug: "bridge",
      image: "bridge.jpg",
      id: 4,
      description:
        "Bridge Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Bridge Defence",
          slug: "bridge1",
          image: "bridge1.jpg",
          description:
            "Two on Final (A & B), one back at Second (C), one near the boots hut (D), other two defend the beach (E & F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Beach",
          slug: "bridge2",
          image: "bridge2.jpg",
          description:
            ""
        },
        {
          name: "Second Assault Entrance",
          slug: "bridge3",
          image: "bridge3.jpg",
          description:
            ""
        },
        {
          name: "Final Assault Entrance",
          slug: "bridge4",
          image: "bridge4.jpg",
          description:
            "One outside (A), one Final (B), rest low. If A needs help, B goes up to the bridge and helps."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "ColderSteelPE",
      slug: "colder",
      image: "colder.jpg",
      id: 5,
      description:
        "ColderSteelPE Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Glass & Hydraulic Pump",
          slug: "colder1",
          image: "colder1.jpg",
          description:
            "One back left side (A), one front left side (B). Three in the middle (C, D & E), one right side (F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Laser Field",
          slug: "colder2",
          image: "colder2.jpg",
          description:
            "Two defending each side (A & B left, C & D right), one in the nest in the middle (E), last one defending the Supply Lift (F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Hangar Doors",
          slug: "colder3",
          image: "colder3.jpg",
          description:
            "One sniper nest (A), two Hangar Door 1 (B & C), rest Hangar Door 2 (D, E & F), keep an eye out for attackers coming from the top left (x)."
        },
        {
          name: "Crew Quarters",
          slug: "colder4",
          image: "colder4.jpg",
          description:
            "Two left side front (A & B), two right side front (C & D), one back low left (E), one back low right (F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Base",
          slug: "colder5",
          image: "colder5.jpg",
          description:
            "One sniper nest defending against launchers/jumpers on the hill (A), one back inside underneath the ventilation drop down (B), rest push out. (C, D, E, F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Base",
          slug: "colder6",
          image: "colder6.jpg",
          description:
            "One sniper nest defending against launchers/jumpers on the hill (A), one back inside underneath the ventilation drop down (B), rest push out. (C, D, E, F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Final",
          slug: "colder7",
          image: "colder7.jpg",
          description:
            "One at the back (A), rest push."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Desertstorm",
      slug: "desert",
      image: "desert.jpg",
      id: 7,
      description:
        "Desertstorm Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Samsite",
          slug: "desert1",
          image: "desert1.jpg",
          description:
            "One back low (A), one back high window (B), two ramps (C & D), one in front of the spawn (E), one flag room (F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Final",
          slug: "desert2",
          image: "desert2.jpg",
          description:
            "One back low (A take the belt (x)), two high (B & C), rest push."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Desolate][",
      slug: "deso",
      image: "deso.jpg",
      id: 8,
      description:
        "Desolate][] Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Start",
          slug: "deso1",
          image: "deso1.jpg",
          description:
            "Attackers will set a double hammer launch (y) to the switch. Tactics aren't necessary for this part. Keep an eye on the hill on the left for jumpers (x)."
        },
        {
          name: "Generator Room",
          slug: "deso2",
          image: "deso2.jpg",
          description:
            "One back low (A), one back high (B, take the belt in spawn), one push low armor (C), one near the ramp (D), rest push high (E & F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Guard Room",
          slug: "deso3",
          image: "deso3.jpg",
          description:
            "Two back at the switch (A & B), two pushing left (C & D), rest pushing right (E & F)."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "DustbowlAL",
      slug: "dust",
      image: "dust.jpg",
      id: 9,
      description:
        "DustbowlAL Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Start Area",
          slug: "dust1",
          image: "dust1.jpg",
          description:
            "Defenders can take the left-most teleport to the Sniper Nest (X). Attackers can open a side route (Y opens Y1) to get easier access to the first objective and new spawn (Z). Attackers can launch or hammerjump high at (L)."
        },
        {
          name: "Main Gate Area",
          slug: "dust1",
          image: "dust1.jpg",
          description:
            "This area holds a fair number of experiences that are needed to move on through the map. Attackers need both Main Gate Lasers (X) and Main Gate Switch (Y) to get their new spawn, so those are the vital experiences. You'll want one on top of the main gate wall, watching for launchers and sneakers (A), one backman (B) at the Main Gate Lasers (X), one backman (C) at the Gate Switch (Y). Rest push out."
        },
        {
          name: "Innerbase",
          slug: "dust3",
          image: "dust3.jpg",
          description:
            "One back at the entrance to the inner base (A). One on the roof of defender spawn, watching for hammerjumpers on the right (B). Rest push out. Attackers will rocket launch from their spawn (X)."
        },
        {
          name: "Generators",
          slug: "dust4",
          image: "dust4.jpg",
          description:
            "One watching the back entrance (A), one defending the generators (B), rest push out. Attackers will launch from (x)."
        },
        {
          name: "Final",
          slug: "dust5",
          image: "dust5.jpg",
          description:
            "One (A) watching the sewers (y), taking the boots (x). One watching the hammerlaunch on the right (B), one at the back (C), rest push out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "GolgothaAL",
      slug: "golgo-al",
      image: "golgo-al.jpg",
      id: 10,
      description:
        "GolgothaAL Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Hurons Temple/Undead",
          slug: "golgo-al1",
          image: "golgo-al1.jpg",
          description:
            "At the start, you'll need at least two people (A & B) sniping high until Undead is reached. You don't want the attackers to launch to the Hurons Path (X), as that's the toughest part of the map to attack. Defenders can take the 'Right Tower' teleport to snipe from there (Y). Attackers will attempt a double hammer launch from the 'flower' (Z) after they get the Temple Doors open."
        },
        {
          name: "Hurons Path",
          slug: "golgo-al2",
          image: "golgo-al2.jpg",
          description:
            "One outside (A), one in the box (B), two on the bridge sniping (C & D), rest push down the stairs (E & F). If A needs help, B will help. C falls back to the box until outside is clear."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Golgotha][AL",
      slug: "golgo2",
      image: "golgo2-al.jpg",
      id: 11,
      description:
        "Golgotha][AL Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Gate Switch",
          slug: "golgo2-al1",
          image: "golgo2-al1.jpg",
          description:
            "Two front left (A & B), one back left (C), two front right (D & E), one back right (F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Lifts",
          slug: "golgo2-al2",
          image: "golgo2-al2.jpg",
          description:
            "One back at the lifts (A), one (B) below watching for launchers near Hurons Sword (X), one (C) defending against launches (Y & Z) to Temple, either by taking the Temple teleport (C1) or backhammering to the start roof (C2). Rest watch low."
        },
        {
          name: "Temple",
          slug: "golgo2-al3",
          image: "golgo2-al3.jpg",
          description:
            "One (A) watching the window, rest push out low."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "LavaFort][PV",
      slug: "lava",
      image: "lava.jpg",
      id: 12,
      description:
        "LavaFort][PV Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Energy Cells",
          slug: "lava1",
          image: "lava1.jpg",
          description:
            "One on top of the wall (A), one back at the entrance to the Lava Cave with the belt (B), rest push out."
        },
        {
          name: "Final",
          slug: "lava2",
          image: "lava2.jpg",
          description:
            "One on top of the wall (A), one at the back (B), rest push through the Main Gate teleport. Attackers can ripper from many spots (X, Y & Z are some of them)."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "LostTemple",
      slug: "lost",
      image: "lost1.jpg",
      id: 13,
      description:
        "LostTemple Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Bridge",
          slug: "lost1",
          image: "lost1.jpg",
          description:
            "One defending the high route (A), one at the back of the bridge (B). After the secret side route (x) is opened, one jumps down and defends the boots (C). Rest push."
        },
        {
          name: "Chains",
          slug: "lost2",
          image: "lost2.jpg",
          description:
            "Two front left (A & B), one back left (C), two front right (D & E), one back right (F). Defenders can take a teleport to a sniper position (X)."
        },
        {
          name: "Switch",
          slug: "lost3",
          image: "lost3.jpg",
          description:
            "One (A) back, rest push out."
        },
        {
          name: "Escape",
          slug: "lost4",
          image: "lost4.jpg",
          description:
            "One (A) back, rest push out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "NaliColony",
      slug: "nali",
      image: "nali.jpg",
      id: 14,
      description:
        "NaliColony Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Virus",
          slug: "nali1",
          image: "nali1.jpg",
          description:
            "At the start, everyone takes the Wall teleporter. Two should push to kill the launches (x)."
        },
        {
          name: "Hydraulic System",
          slug: "nali2",
          image: "nali2.jpg",
          description:
            "One (A) taking the boots in the garage (x) and defending the top left wall against rocket shooters (Y) and jumpers to the Sniper Nest (Z). Two people (B & C) defending the objective, two (D & E) push, and one (F) near the wall. If attackers jump the Sniper Nest, A and D suicide and chase."
        },
        {
          name: "Train",
          slug: "nali3",
          image: "nali3.jpg",
          description:
            "Two (A & B) back at the Train, rest push. Keep an eye out for attackers sneaking through defender's spawn."
        },
        {
          name: "Teleport Switches",
          slug: "nali4",
          image: "nali4.jpg",
          description:
            "Three front right (A, B & C), three front left (D, E & F). Attackers can lower the glass in the middle by touching the panels next to the windows (X & Y), but defenders can raise the glass again by touching the same panels."
        },
        {
          name: "Blue and Red Chains",
          slug: "nali5",
          image: "nali5.jpg",
          description:
            "Everyone takes the Outside teleport. Attackers can trigger a new spawn by reaching the Castle Entrance (x), also disabling the Outside teleport. Choose one of the chains to defend with everyone, ignore the other."
        },
        {
          name: "Orb",
          slug: "nali6",
          image: "nali6.jpg",
          description:
            "One back left (A), one back right (B), rest push."
        },
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Riverbed]I[AL",
      slug: "riv3",
      image: "riv3al.jpg",
      id: 15,
      description:
        "Riverbed]I[AL Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Tunnels",
          slug: "riv3al1",
          image: "riv3al1.jpg",
          description:
            "One back at tunnels (A), one in front of the box (B) giving incomings, rest push out. Attackers might camp the spawn from the right ledge (X)."
        },
        {
          name: "Charge",
          slug: "riv3al2",
          image: "riv3al2.jpg",
          description:
            "Two defending high (A & B), rest defending low."
        },
        {
          name: "Radio",
          slug: "riv3al3",
          image: "riv3al3.jpg",
          description:
            "One defending high (A), one back low (B), one sniping from the tower (C), rest push out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Siege][",
      slug: "siege",
      image: "siege.jpg",
      id: 16,
      description:
        "Siege][ Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Final",
          slug: "siege1",
          image: "siege1.jpg",
          description:
            "Two on the roof (A & B), two inside (C & D. D hammercamping the teleport exit). E & F outside stopping/giving warnings for launches (x, y & z)."
        },
        {
          name: "Inside",
          slug: "siege2",
          image: "siege2.jpg",
          description:
            "Two inside (C & D. D hammercamping the teleport exit)."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "Submarinebase][",
      slug: "subbase",
      image: "subbase.jpg",
      id: 17,
      description:
        "Submarinebase][ Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Ventilation",
          slug: "subbase1",
          image: "subbase1.jpg",
          description:
            "One back at the objective with belt/keg (A), one under the glass (B), two in the main room (C & D). Rest push."
        },
        {
          name: "Gate",
          slug: "subbase2",
          image: "subbase2.jpg",
          description:
            "One on the bridge (A), one defending the side route (B), rest push to main room, taking belt/keg."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "TheDungeon]I[AL",
      slug: "dungeon",
      image: "dungeon.jpg",
      id: 18,
      description:
        "TheDungeon]I[AL Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Lake",
          slug: "dungeon1",
          image: "dungeon1.jpg",
          description:
            "One back low (A), one defending high route (B throwing down a shock rifle to A first run). Rest low."
        },
        {
          name: "Falls",
          slug: "dungeonl2",
          image: "dungeon2.jpg",
          description:
            "One back at the Falls (A), one defending shock (B), one taking the boots (x) and defending near flak (C). Two taking the teleport and pushing (D & E), one pushing low bridge (F)."
        },
        {
          name: "Skull Lock",
          slug: "dungeon3",
          image: "dungeon3.jpg",
          description:
            "One watching spawn (A), one back at the objective (B), two defending high (C & D), rest low."
        },
        {
          name: "Escape",
          slug: "dungeon4",
          image: "dungeon4.jpg",
          description:
            "One watching the side tunnel (A), two at the back (B & C), one front left (D), one front right (E), one middle/freelance (F)."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name: "TheScarabSE",
      slug: "scarab",
      image: "scarab.jpg",
      id: 19,
      description:
        "TheScarabSE Tactics",
      experiences: [
        {
          name: "Guard House Switch",
          slug: "scarab1",
          image: "scarab1.jpg",
          description:
            "One taking the Entrance teleporter and defending the Base (A), one taking the Base teleporter and going up to the Sniper Tower (B), rest take the Outside teleporter (first run only) and defend the objective (x)."
        },
        {
          name: "Enemy Base",
          slug: "scarab2",
          image: "scarab2.jpg",
          description:
            "One defending the base (A), one taking the Base teleporter and defending the Elevator Window (B), rest push out (Use the Entrance teleporter). If attackers breach Sniper Tower (y) or Elevator Window (z), B and someone else suicide and chase. Attackers can drop down a vent into Enemy Base at (x)."
        },
        {
          name: "Hangar Doors",
          slug: "scarab3",
          image: "scarab3.jpg",
          description:
            "One back at the switch (A), one (B) defending the left side, taking the belt. One defending against launches low left (C), two pushing high (D & E), one pushing low (F) until attackers get Sniper Tower Door (y). After that watch for sneakers through the spawn (F1)."
        },
        {
          name: "Hangar Doors - 2",
          slug: "scarab4",
          image: "scarab4.jpg",
          description:
            "One back at the switch (A), one (B) defending the left side, taking the belt. One defending against launches low left (C), two pushing high (D & E), one pushing low (F) until attackers get Sniper Tower Door (y). After that watch for sneakers through the spawn (F1)."
        },
        {
          name: "Ship",
          slug: "scarab5",
          image: "scarab5.jpg",
          description:
            "One back low (A), one back high (B), one spawn defending the switch to open high route (C), one at the top of the jump pad (D), rest push out."
        },
        {
          name: "Ship - Outside",
          slug: "scarab6",
          image: "scarab6.jpg",
          description:
            "One back low (A), one back high (B), one spawn defending the switch to open high route (C), one at the top of the jump pad (D), rest push out."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
};
